WEBVTT

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:33.576
I will give my opinion which you
may or may not agree with.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.416
Us: then both of us will, together,

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:38.376
try and find a solution
to the problem in which we both win.

00:05:38.400 --> 00:05:40.936
Whatever the age, whatever
the problem, larger issues

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:44.776
like depression, anxiety or drugs
or everyday struggles

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:50.616
like homework, studies, television --
we should work with our children, not against them.

00:05:50.640 --> 00:05:53.656
We parents have a lot
of dreams for our children.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:56.856
"He will you achieve all that I could not."

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:59.576
“I sacrificed my life for you,

00:05:59.600 --> 00:06:02.056
now you cannot let me down”.